title: EARTH WIND AND FIRE - NOW, THEN AND FOREVER
description:
EARTH WIND AND FIRE...Now what group you know at the mere mention of their name sparks the comment THEY ARE BAD!!!!!

Earth Wind and Fire has been around for a number of decades and has not failed to please the listening audience in all of that time. From Phillip Bailey's high notes to Maurice Whites commanding vocals EWF has always pleased and here we have them again in 2013 sending continued shivers down the listeners ears with their new release NOW, THEN AND FOREVER

Enjoy the 2013 experience from EWF

Album Tracks

	  1. Sign On
	  2. Love is Law	
	  3. My Promise	 
	  4. Guiding Lights

	  8. Splashes	 
          9. Night of My Life	 
	  10. The Rush
